### VS Code REST Client Examples
### Install the REST Client extension to use this file

### Get all games
GET http://localhost:8000/api/games

###

### Get new releases
GET http://localhost:8000/api/games/new-releases

###

### Get highest rated games
GET http://localhost:8000/api/games/highest-rated

###

### Search for a specific game
GET http://localhost:8000/api/games/search?title=Minecraft

###

### Filter games by genre
GET http://localhost:8000/api/games/genre?genre=RPG

###

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

###

### Get request logs
GET http://localhost:8000/__logs

###

### Reload configuration
POST http://localhost:8000/__reload

###

### Custom config - Orders endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders?page=1&limit=10

###

### Custom config - Auth login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpass"
}
